Package fr.diginamic.entities.associatives

Class WordingSport

java.lang.Object
fr.diginamic.entities.associatives.WordingSport
@Entity public class WordingSport extends Object
Represents a WordingSport in the system. A WordingSport is a name of a Sport in a specific language. Table associatives between Sport and Langue.
